855
00:59:08,520 --> 00:59:10,840
that you're just pretending.

856
00:59:10,840 --> 00:59:13,320
If someone saw you, they'd say you're being jealous.

857
00:59:13,320 --> 00:59:15,080
Why are you so into it, for nothing?

858
00:59:15,080 --> 00:59:17,080
When was I jeal??

859
00:59:25,600 --> 00:59:26,600
Oh.

860
00:59:31,120 --> 00:59:33,000
I am jealous.

861
00:59:36,280 --> 00:59:37,800
What do you mean?

862
00:59:42,680 --> 00:59:44,120
I was jealous.

863
00:59:53,640 --> 00:59:55,160
This pretend relationship??

864
00:59:57,800 --> 00:59:59,360
I'd better end it here.

865
01:00:01,680 --> 01:00:04,720
Choi Da-in, you're so pathetic.

