01:01:43,360 --> 01:01:44,680
You know something?

872
01:01:45,440 --> 01:01:49,120
Ryan wants to end this fake relationship.

873
01:02:01,440 --> 01:02:04,480
Curator Sung, there's something I want to say to you.

874
01:02:04,480 --> 01:02:06,200
Come down to the parking lot.

875
01:02:19,760 --> 01:02:21,000
I like you.

