883
01:03:36,400 --> 01:03:39,720
There's something I wanted to say to you.

884
01:03:41,880 --> 01:03:44,880
I know it's sudden, but Curator Sung??

885
01:03:44,880 --> 01:03:46,040
Director.

886
01:03:48,920 --> 01:03:50,640
However, a love confession

887
01:03:52,120 --> 01:03:54,760
