895
01:04:31,880 --> 01:04:32,880
Curator Sung.

896
01:04:33,240 --> 01:04:34,280
Curator Sung??

897
01:04:43,280 --> 01:04:44,800
My confession??

898
01:04:46,680 --> 01:04:49,080
