904
01:06:43,120 --> 01:06:44,240
Curator Sung.

905
01:06:44,240 --> 01:06:46,080
As you can see, I'm a bit busy.

906
01:06:46,080 --> 01:06:47,080
They're the ones who broke up,

907
01:06:47,080 --> 01:06:50,080
