911
01:06:55,080 --> 01:06:57,360
How could I get dumped when I didn't even go out with her?

912
01:06:57,360 --> 01:06:59,160
I need to make this clear.

913
01:06:59,160 --> 01:07:00,560
If you don't have anything to say, I??

